title: |md
  ## Algorithm Steps: H0..H7 Initial Values — Square Root Derivation
  **FIPS 180-4 §5.3.3 · "Nothing Up My Sleeve" Numbers**
| {near: top-center}
classes: {
  prime_cell: {
    style: {
      fill: "#E8D5F5"
      stroke: "#7B2D8B"
      stroke-width: 2
      font: mono
